# User Role Full-Stack Implementation

When implementing or updating user role and permission features, complete the full flow in the same task.

- Create or update the controller logic.
- Create or update web routes.
- Create or update related models.
- Create or update required migrations.
- Create or update the UI/front-end pages.
- Ensure the user role page is reachable from the sidebar navigation.
- Keep all role-related changes scoped to the user role feature/pages so the behavior works end-to-end.
